reviewText: Guess I was expecting something different. It was so boring I couldn't finish it.
L.R.in his prime play-riding with his buds. Picture and sound quality not great. Worth the watch for sentimental value. Alot has changed since this was videoed.

I watched it through Amazon Prime, It was unwatchable!
I wasted my money.
Buy Knighter the Iron Man of Enduro.
Nathen Woods  Offroad was good also.

Amazon says they will give me my money back on this.
Thank you to Amazon.
